com.lousylynx.otfl.library.util

Class FMLInjector

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lousylynx.otfl.library.util.FMLInjector

  • public class FMLInjector
extends java.lang.Object
    This class injects itself into the Minecraft source code, to retrieve objects required to fix specific errors that have to do with registries.

    • Method Detail

      • inject

        public static void inject()
        This method should never be called by an addon to the api. This is the method that begins the injection into the code. This method is called by the OnTheFly main class, and will throw an error if you try to call it again.
